text: It's now located nearer to the Novena church side of the road, due to the insane road works happening in front and around Velocity Mall. No shelter, dusty roads, warm everywhere, and a short walk away from the actual MRT station. Just be more mindful and scrappy, and you'll be fine managing your transit.
spend 20min walking under the rain just to find out that the train station is not behind the busstop but you have to walk towards the mall to get to the station
